Class OpportunityController

java.lang.Object
edu.cnm.deepdive.tvnservice.controller.OpportunityController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/organizations/{organizationId}/opportunities") public class OpportunityController extends Object
Handles REST requests for operation on individual instances and collections of Opportunity entity.
